   KEY INFORMATION ABOUT GOLF TODAY  
 
 
 Online since November 1996 
 Europe's premier online golf magazine  
 Over 8 million visitors per annum 
 65% of readers from the UK and Ireland 
 18% of readers from Continental Europe 
 11% of readers from North America 
 6% of readers from Asia, Australasia, Africa and South America 
 The world's most comprehensive and permanently updated Course Guide  
 More than  55,000 pages of content, archived and searchable 
 Consistently high ranking on all major search engines for golf-related enquiries 
 Widely consulted by journalists as a work of reference 
 Heavily used by travelling golfers to find a new course, a golf holiday, tee-times and bargain green fee deals 
 
 


 
  
 
  
   
 
